albacore
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Thunnus alalungs</i>, (previously listed as <i>Germo germon</i>, <i>Thunnus germo</i>, and variants) fam. Scombridae, a moderate-sized tuna widely distributed in the world's oceans.  See also tuna.  Also known as long-finned albacore.
