Author: SORENSEN
Vol / Page: 9
Edition:
Quote: ALBACORE (see also Tuna) (a) Scientific name: <i>Thunnus alaunga</i>. (b) Suggested commercial name: Albacore. (c) Other common names: Tuna, Tunny, long-finned albacore. (d) Principal localities where taken: Bay of Plenty, East Cape to Gisborne, North Taranaki Bight.
Notes:

Date: 0/0/1981
