Author: WILSON
Vol / Page: 19
Edition:
Quote: ALBACORE ... Some confusion reigns as to this fellow's real name. As with many of our fish he has several. His scientific name can either be <i>Thunnus germo</i> or <i>Thunnus alalungs</i>, depending onwhich authority you believe. Common names include Southern Bluefin, Longfin-Tuna and Longfin Albacore. ...
